裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"38a0217f3bd6f656bbddee8c3689873cbaf957e3","tid":1538990,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"快啦騙子"},{"pid":"622be045202c4621880a87cb3a2734303516972d","tid":1538990,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"摺被"},{"pid":"27fc5440d838a8317995f47e3b963398e293e891","tid":1538990,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"a5c09f120a5d3c625c179b7280444b3b09a9c2b6","tid":1538990,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"係咪中秋佢哋嚟買月餅炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae660d7107814e1bf6cc7f8c65456d97e65f42ec","tid":1538990,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:49.000Z","msg":"炒月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7df2e3abd4366b1f7c04cba7f65f7fbfc30cc3","tid":1538990,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:58:20.000Z","msg":"好似佢哋上次澳洲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6c9e02eee722d4b24dadd306b3cc9a2990b6f3","tid":1538990,"uid":260271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"出pla?<br />\n攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas